info.name: DarkBash
info.description: A dark theme for various Bash sites.
info.additionalInfo: Supported Sites: http://ibash.de http://ibash.org.ru http://www.bash.org http://qdb.us http://german-bash.org http://bash.org.pl http://bash.im http://www.xkcdb.com http://tjbash.org http://danstonchat.com http://school-bash.org http://nya.sh I originally wanted to include a custom font, but unfortunately there doesn't seem to be a way to get Google Fonts to work with Stylish for Firefox (if you want to publish a style, you have to do that in the Firefox format). However, if you're using Chrome, you can still get the "full" version here.
